section
  :markdown
    ## Embedding
    - Use [`<iframe>`][0] for embedding content
      - nested browsing context
      - [content security policy][4]
      - [sandbox][3]ing and isolation

    - PlugIns still use [`<object>`][1] and [`<embed>`][2] tags
      - look at the [oembed][] standard
      - and [embed.ly][] supporting 250+ providers
    
    [0]: http://developers.whatwg.org/the-iframe-element.html
    [1]: http://developers.whatwg.org/the-iframe-element.html#the-object-element
    [2]: http://developers.whatwg.org/the-iframe-element.html#the-embed-element
    [3]: http://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/security/sandboxed-iframes/
    [4]: http://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/security/content-security-policy/
    [oembed]: http://oembed.com/
    [embed.ly]: http://embed.ly/

