section
  :markdown
    ## Graphics: 2D Canvas

    - [`<canvas>` element][0]
      - provides a fixed size drawing surface
      - rendering APIs
      - stateful context
      - [All major browsers after IE8][3]

    - [2D Rendering Context][1]
      - paths, rectangles, images and text
      - strokes & fills: colors, gradients, images, patterns
      - transforms: translate, scale, rotate, matrix
      - image generation with [`toDataURL()`][2]

    [0]: http://developers.whatwg.org/the-canvas-element.html
    [1]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D
    [2]: http://developers.whatwg.org/the-canvas-element.html#dom-canvas-todataurl
    [3]: http://caniuse.com/#feat=canvas

