    ## Video and Audio
    a nightmare of [politics, formats & proprietary codecs][0]

    - [`<video>`][1]
      - MP4: _IE, Chrome, Safari, iOS, Android_
      - WebM: _Chrome, Firefox, Opera_
    - [`<audio>`][2]
      - AAC: _IE, Chrome, Safari, iOS, Android_
      - MP3: _IE, Chrome, Safari, iOS, Android_
      - Vorbis: _Chrome, Firefox, Opera_
    - [`<source>`][3] for alternate formats
      - use with media queries
    - [`<track>`][4] for timed text or data feeds
        
    [0]: http://www.longtailvideo.com/html5/
    [1]: http://caniuse.com/video
    [2]: http://caniuse.com/audio
    [3]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/source
    [4]: http://www.longtailvideo.com/blog/27621/whats-new-in-html5-the-track-element/

